data.description: With brand new exterior paint and an almost new driveway this 3 bedroom tri-level with a lower level room that  could be a 4th bedroom.  Hardwood floors on main level in great condition .   Good size living room with bay windows and a walk out to rear yard from family room.  Fireplace in family room.  Ready for a quick move in and its next owners.
